http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/One-killed-four-injured-in-accident/article14021927.ece

A man was killed and four others injured after a bus rammed a van at Movady Cross on NH-66 in Kundapur taluk on Monday.The deceased has been identified as Mamith Poojary.According to the police, Mamith, who was driving the van, was going from Hemmady to Maravanthe with his friends Dinesh Poojary, Ganesh Mogaveera, Keshav, and Mahesh from Hemmady to Maravanthe, when the private bus rammed it.Mamith was rushed to Kasturba Hospital in Manipal, where he died.The others have been admitted to a private hospital in Kundapur.A case had been registered at Gangolli police station, the police said.